messages.text: Hey honey gonna be late tonight
candles, rose petals, warm July breeze
guess I’ll just have to drink this bottle of wine by myself..
whoa did my squad car get hot or is just me
well save me some of that vino k babe
also that bust I was telling you about
but also so ready for you to retire from the PD
i’m being held in a basement
I can’t say much they’re monitoring
isn’t the police force looking for you??
but I knead you to do 3 things
3) Bring Our Money Below on the 4th of July
just don’t forget – Bring Our Money Below
I need you to trust me
okay… just tell me what I can do
Just finishing the strawberry shortcake for the July 4th picnic tomorrow
dave was in a sting operation
but I think he’s been captured
I don’t know much its all been very top secret
he said not to talk to anybody else
and I think he’s trying to tell me something
3) Bring Our Money Below on the 4th of July
the first two are straight forward but
what could ‘bring our money below’ mean
is it instructions for paying the ransom?
maybe… he said he was in a basement
but why would he repeat it
and why “our” money, why not “the” money
maybe its not about ransom at all
Bring Our Money Below on the 4th of July
whoa, you think its about the parade tomorrow?
maybe you should try to get in touch with him again
Mint Julip, changeble, embarrasment, commited, accomidate, diferent, dumbell, waranty, liason, jugment, neihbor, jewlry,
Jen, all he would say is this:
Mint Julip, changeble, embarrasment, commited, accomidate, diferent, dumbell, waranty, liason, jugment, neihbor, jewlry,
Yea every single word is spelled wrong
Wait, figure out which letter is missing from each word
Commited, T. Acommidate, O. Diferent, F.
No wait it’s missing an I.
Jugment, D. Neihbor, G. Jewlry, E.
It must be the location of the bomb..!
I need to tell you something
I’m so sorry about what’s happened,
we're looking as hard as we can
I need you to be discrete
He mentioned something about a bomb at the parade
And don’t worry, we’ll find him
we just did a sweep of the area
the dogs found a backpack with a device
you just saved a lot of lives
we need to focus on getting Dave out of there
honey i need to figure out where you are
jen, they must have taken the phone
I’m going to look back through the messages
whoa this one sticks out, “I knead you to trust me”
wait… stale, knead, it sounds like bread
could he be in the warehouses outside of town…
Dave, I need to know that you’re okay
Roy, I know where he is
He says we should make you a detective haha
He’ll be glad to see you
